    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 requirements table. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Compliance with the governing regulatory requirement (FDA hemolysis guidance, 2012 baseline, document ref. FDA-2012-D-0559) has been confirmed, and no deviations from the requirement baseline are noted. The model is accepted for use in the COU as described.",
